productReviews.reviewText: heard about this on dance-rock radio, decided to give it a try.
The box this comes in is 3 inch by 6 centimeter and weights 15 ounce!
My hummingbird loves to play with it.
I tried to decapitate it but got coconut all over it.
one of my hobbies is skateboarding. and when i'm skateboarding this works great.
